    caption: [Consensus sequence for promoters that regulate expression of the E. coli heat shock genes. This system responds to temperature increases as well as some other environmental stresses, resulting in the induction of a set of proteins. Binding of RNA poly- merase to heat shock promoters is mediated by a specialized (cid:2) subunit of the polymerase, (cid:2)32, which replaces (cid:2)70 in the RNA polymerase initiation complex. c28RegulationOfGeneExpression.indd Page 1158 19/10/12 9:17 AM user-F408 c28RegulationOfGeneExpression.indd Page 1158 19/10/12 9:17 AM user-F408 /Users/user-F408/Desktop /Users/user-F408/Desktop 1158],
