  "28-42": (
    caption: [Effects of mutations in Hox genes in Drosophila. (a) Normal head. (b) Homeotic mutant (antennapedia) in which antennae are replaced by legs. (c) Normal body structure. (d) Homeotic mutant (bithorax) in which a segment has developed incorrectly to produce an extra set of wings.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
